data.description: Welcome to this move-in-ready home nestled in the High Timbers neighborhood of Charlotte! Boasting 4 bedrooms and 2.5 bathrooms, this home is designed for both comfort and style. The main level showcases the primary bedroom and a guest suite, ensuring convenience and accessibility. The home's interior offers a seamless flow throughout, highlighted by a vaulted ceiling in the family room with a charming fireplace and hearth, spacious living room and dining room, and generously sized bedrooms. The kitchen features a large breakfast area, lots of cabinets, solid surface countertops, and a convenient closet laundry room. New carpet upstairs, fresh coat of paint throughout. Enjoy the covered patio surrounded by mature trees. Convenient to shopping, hospitals, and restaurants. Walk to McAlpine Greenway and minutes from downtown Matthews.
